" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3613096\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3613096\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fqh1665702641252.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fqh1665702641252.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fqh1665702641252.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fqh1665702641252\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Tab Orientation (\n                              TabOrientation)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Orientation of the tab strip. The default is <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Horizontal</code>.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__p_d107882e1_d107883e1_d107884e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>TabOrientation<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Horizontal</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">Accordion</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">Stack</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__table_d12710e1_d12711e1_d12712e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__table_d12710e1_d12711e1_d12712e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__table_d12710e1_d12711e1_d12712e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fqh1665702641252__table_d12710e1_d12711e1_d12712e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Horizontal</code> (default)</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fqh1665702641252__table_d12710e1_d12711e1_d12712e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Tab strip is displayed horizontally.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fqh1665702641252__table_d12710e1_d12711e1_d12712e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Accordion</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fqh1665702641252__table_d12710e1_d12711e1_d12712e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Tab strip is displayed as a vertical stack, with the contained form displayed immediately below the selected tab.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fqh1665702641252__table_d12710e1_d12711e1_d12712e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Stack</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fqh1665702641252__table_d12710e1_d12711e1_d12712e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Tab strip is displayed as a vertical stack, with the contained form displayed above or below the stack (depending on the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Position</span> property).</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__section_v1l_2c2_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d425091e163\">Usage</h2>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__section_bxh_fc2_1xb\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__table_d11987e1_d11988e1_d11989e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__section_v2r_fc2_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d425091e212\">Using in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__p_d107891e1_d107892e1_d107893e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span> or\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span> to set or get the property and its value. For\n            more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zie1665702558978.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zie1665702558978.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of a field.\">$properties</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aud1705998763272.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1705998763272.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field.\">$fieldproperties</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__pre_t5h_hc2_1xb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD) = \"taborientation=accordion\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__section_ndn_hc2_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d425091e245\">Example: Accordion Tabs</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__p_d107897e1_d107898e1_d107899e1\">When <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Orientation</span> is set\n            to <code class=\"ph codeph\">Accordion</code>, the resulting tab widget displays the contained form\n            below the selected tab; in the following illustration case, it is the Component Editor\n            tab. (In this example, the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Height</span> has also been set to 3\n            characters.)</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__fig_d107900e1_d107901e1_d107902e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Accordion Tabs</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Image\" class=\"image\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__image_jy1_lc2_1xb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/tabaccordion.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__section_e35_lc2_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d425091e275\">Example: Stacked Tabs</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__p_d107909e1_d107910e1_d107911e1\">By default, a tab stack is displayed above the\n            contained form. It can often be preferable to position it below the form because it\n            focuses more attention on the form content than the tabs themselves.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__p_d107912e1_d107913e1_d107914e1\">The following ProcScript sets the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab\n               Orientation</span> to <code class=\"ph codeph\">stack</code>, the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab\n               Position</span> to <code class=\"ph codeph\">bottom</code>, and the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab\n               Height</span> to <code class=\"ph codeph\">3</code> (characters).</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__pre_mdd_4c2_1xb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vProperties = \"\" ; string variable to contain the widget properties\nputitem/id vProperties,\"taborientation\",\"stack\"\nputitem/id vProperties,\"tabpos\",\"bottom\"\nputitem/id vProperties,\"tabheight\",\"3\"\n$fieldproperties(TABFIELD) = vProperties</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__p_d107915e1_d107916e1_d107917e1\">In the following illustration, the Presentation tab\n            is selected.</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__fig_d107918e1_d107919e1_d107920e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 2. </span>Stacked Tabs</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Image\" class=\"image\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__image_evf_pc2_1xb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/tabstack_bottom.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fqh1665702641252__section_lfs_qc2_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d425091e325\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gyf1688451219719.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gyf1688451219719.html\" title=\"The utabex widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. The utabex widget is highly customizable, allowing extensive control over the appearance and behavior of the tabs. Uniface provides a logical widget called TabEx, which is mapped to utabex.\">utabex (TabEx)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wme1665702641178.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Tab Position (TabPos)</a><p>The Tab Position widget property determines where the tab strip is located. By default, it is Top.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613096\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613096\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Tab Orientation ( TabOrientation) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Tab Orientation ( TabOrientation) Orientation of the tab strip. The default is Horizontal . \" TabOrientation = Horizontal | Accordion | Stack \" Value Description Horizontal (default) Tab strip is displayed horizontally. Accordion Tab strip is displayed as a vertical stack, with the contained form displayed immediately below the selected tab. Stack Tab strip is displayed as a vertical stack, with the contained form displayed above or below the stack (depending on the Tab Position property). Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: None Using in ProcScript You can use $properties or $fieldproperties to set or get the property and its value. For more information, see $properties and $fieldproperties . $fieldproperties(FLD) = \"taborientation=accordion\" Copy Example: Accordion Tabs When Tab Orientation is set to Accordion , the resulting tab widget displays the contained form below the selected tab; in the following illustration case, it is the Component Editor tab. (In this example, the Tab Height has also been set to 3 characters.) Figure 1. Accordion Tabs Example: Stacked Tabs By default, a tab stack is displayed above the contained form. It can often be preferable to position it below the form because it focuses more attention on the form content than the tabs themselves. The following ProcScript sets the Tab Orientation to stack , the Tab Position to bottom , and the Tab Height to 3 (characters). vProperties = \"\" ; string variable to contain the widget properties putitem/id vProperties,\"taborientation\",\"stack\" putitem/id vProperties,\"tabpos\",\"bottom\" putitem/id vProperties,\"tabheight\",\"3\" $fieldproperties(TABFIELD) = vProperties Copy In the following illustration, the Presentation tab is selected. Figure 2. Stacked Tabs Applies To utabex (TabEx) Related Links Tab Position (TabPos) The Tab Position widget property determines where the tab strip is located. By default, it is Top. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}